# GitHub personal access token (read-only scope recommended)
# Format: https://oauth2:<YOUR_GITHUB_PAT>@github.com
#
# To create a token:
#   1. Go to https://github.com/settings/tokens
#   2. Generate a new token (classic) with 'repo' (read) scope
#   3. Replace <YOUR_GITHUB_PAT> below with the generated token
#
https://oauth2:<YOUR_GITHUB_PAT>@github.com
